{
  "stem": "15962.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But generally speaking, I seem to have the image that I was more or less on my own.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because despite the fact that I had reasonably pair of shoes than the average, I was lagging behind.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I could hear the shots.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because whoever couldn't walk fast enough was-- and lagged behind-- was shot.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the whole road was lined with dead bodies with completely fractured heads.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The-- the SS guards would put the guns close to your head and completely blow you.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Most of them were walking you know, along and behind.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we were three days and two nights or three nights and two days on-- on this horrible journey.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One night, we stayed in some barns and the next night in some open space.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was this-- one of the horrible feelings was that we were crossing the countryside where people lived normal lives.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were passing homes where people slept in normal beds and set their tables and ate food and had families.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I think there was always this feeling of being trapped and being different and helpless situation, while the rest of the world was unwilling to recognize the situation.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This was-- this-- I'm not talking here in generalities.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "General This was the sort of frustrating feeling that followed me for quite a while.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And also is-- later on, became well-known that the allies were unwilling to recognize the need either to bomb the crematoria or to do something about it.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But the population was totally apathetic and would not, in any way, extend a helping hand.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember that we encountered any people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because the Germans closed all the roads so there wouldn't be anybody walking either against us or with us.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
